# Lab 03 - IP Addressing Practice

## Objective

Configure IPv4 addresses on four computers connected through a switch and verify connectivity using the ping command.

---

## Devices Used

- Cisco 2960 Switch
- Admin-PC
- HR-PC
- Finance-PC
- IT-PC

---

## IP Address Configuration

Admin-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.10

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

HR-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.20

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

Finance-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.30

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

IT-PC

IP Address: 192.168.1.40

Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0

---

## Verification

Ping test was performed successfully between the computers.

---

## Result

All devices communicated successfully within the same network.

---

## Skills Learned

- IPv4 Address Configuration
- LAN Communication
- Ping Testing
- Basic Switch Connectivity

